title: Grateful Dead Live at USAir Arena on 1994-10-11

description:
Set 1

Picasso Moon, Jack A Roe, It's All Over Now, High Time*, If The Shoe Fits, Lazy River Road, Easy Answers, Deal

Set 2

Eyes Of The World-> Women Are Smarter-> Samba In The Rain-> He's Gone-> Jam-> Jerry & drummers-> Jerry-> Jam-> (Jerry left for a little bit, then came back out), China Doll**-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Lucy in the Sky

* Weir on acoustic guitar. ** Last played 9/18/93
